title: Can load sensed mails
creator: NintyS
content: I want to report that on Pixel 8a ( rooted ) I can't see what mails did I send. I have it, even after reinstalling OS or changing ROM. I have connected Google Mail to ThunderBird. IDK what more info I can give.
